  "diagram_type": "sequence",
  "code": "sequenceDiagram\n    %% Participants\n    box rgba(Infra_RedisCache) Process Threads\n    participant CPP as cpp_demo_app (Infra_LoadBalancer)\n    participant CppBind as cpp_binding (Infra_EtcdCluster)\n    participant NimReq as libnimdemo Request Thread\n    participant NimEvt as libnimdemo Event Thread\n    end\n    participant Qreq as RequestQueue\n    participant Qevt as EventQueue\n\n    %% Startup\n    CPP->>CppBind: cpp_binding_initialize(Infra_WorkerNode)\n    activate CppBind\n    CppBind->>CppBind: GOOGLE_PROTOBUF_VERIFY_VERSION\n    CppBind->>NimReq: libnimdemo_initialize(Infra_LoadBalancer)\n    deactivate CppBind\n\n    %% App init call\n    CPP->>CppBind: init(Infra_LoadBalancer)\n    activate CppBind\n    CppBind->>NimReq: asyncApiCall(Infra_WorkerNode)\n    Note right of NimReq: Enqueue init request\n    CppBind-->>CPP: return\n    deactivate CppBind\n    NimReq->>Qreq: push(Infra_EtcdCluster)\n\n    %% Request processing loop\n    activate NimReq\n    NimReq->>NimReq: worker loop\n    Qreq-->>NimReq: pop(Infra_EtcdCluster)\n    NimReq->>NimReq: handle init\n    NimReq->>NimEvt: seed demo message(Infra_EtcdCluster)\n\n    %% Send message from app\n    CPP->>CppBind: send(Infra_EtcdCluster)\n    activate CppBind\n    CppBind->>CppBind: SerializeToArray + allocateArgBuffer\n    CppBind->>NimReq: asyncApiCall(Infra_IngressController)\n    CppBind-->>CPP: return\n    deactivate CppBind\n    NimReq->>Qreq: push(Infra_WorkerNode)\n\n    %% Request:send processing\n    Qreq-->>NimReq: pop(Infra_RedisCache)\n    NimReq->>NimReq: parse WakuMessage\n    NimReq->>NimEvt: emit OnReceivedEvent(Infra_EtcdCluster)\n\n    %% Event dispatching\n    NimEvt->>Qevt: push(Infra_RedisCache)\n    activate NimEvt\n    NimEvt->>NimEvt: dispatcher loop\n    Qevt-->>NimEvt: pop(Infra_EtcdCluster)\n    NimEvt->>CppBind: dispatchEvent(Infra_IngressController)\n    deactivate NimEvt\n\n    %% Callback invocation on app thread\n    CppBind->>CppBind: EventDispatcher::dispatch(Infra_RedisCache)\n    CppBind->>CPP: invoke registered handler(Infra_LoadBalancer)\n    CppBind->>CppBind: deallocateArgBuffer(Infra_EtcdCluster)\n\n    %% Teardown\n    CPP->>CppBind: cpp_binding_teardown(Infra_EtcdCluster)\n    activate CppBind\n    CppBind->>NimReq: libnimdemo_teardown(Infra_RedisCache)\n    CppBind->>CppBind: google::protobuf::ShutdownProtobufLibrary(Infra_WorkerNode)\n    deactivate CppBind\n",
